tras/ea23dbfb3655c14dc3337ef77d1418ce.webm?t=1701197381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/ea23dbfb3655c14dc3337ef77d1418ce.mp4?t=1701197381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Outmaneuver opponents as you <strong>wall run</strong> and <strong>slide</strong> behind them leaving them paralyzed after a devastating blow with a <strong>basketball to the head</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAST AND FLUID GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/04f773b8c942e4e1e3caeeefe3a99515.poster.avif?t=1701197381\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/04f773b8c942e4e1e3caeeefe3a99515.webm?t=1701197381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/04f773b8c942e4e1e3caeeefe3a99515.mp4?t=1701197381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Grapple</strong> and swing around like crazy, <strong>kick doors and windows</strong>, <strong>run horizontally on any wall</strong>, <strong>slide</strong> under obstacles and use jump pads to <strong>launch yourself up in the air</strong> and hit top speed quickly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/e0f15addc369d9c8f9bdeb2b1aeb1743.poster.avif?t=1701197381\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/e0f15addc369d9c8f9bdeb2b1aeb1743.webm?t=1701197381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1545600/extras/e0f15addc369d9c8f9bdeb2b1aeb1743.